from solution import Solution

cases = [
    (13, 4, 2),
    (21, 21, 0),
    (14, 13, -1),
    # more tests
    (1,1,0),
    (2,1,-1),
    (7,3,0), # 7(111) to 3(011): need to change the highest bit -> set it to 0 -> count=1? Wait: n & k == k? 7&3=3==3 OK. diff=7^3=100 ->1 -> answer 1. So expected 1.
]

# fix the above case
cases[-1] = (7,3,1)

s = Solution()

for n,k,exp in cases:
    out = s.minChanges(n,k)
    print(n,k, out, 'OK' if out==exp else 'WRONG expected '+str(exp))
